NEW JERSEY LAND TITLE ASSOCIATION, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Dana RONE, County Register of the County of Essex, Defendant-Petitioner. C-882 September Term 2018
082620 Supreme Court of New Jersey. JUNE 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005028-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted.
